column5: Is it just me or is it a trend with all seelhead fishermen that they take the pic at the  head lookin down its body Either laying on the ground or the angler holding its face in the camera? .. Im not trying to start anything by this , i think its a cool shot but it seems only steelhead i see like that ..
That one either came out of Kama or the Volga river, or somewhere in Ireland.
usual how they come out of the river on tha bank so i pull the hook snap a pic and slide em back home
i'll make sure to do it with a few of my largemouth next season see how it works and with some specks on jan 1st!
